title: The Scottish cavalier;
author: Grant, James
snippet: Young Holsterlee will be at the countess of Dunbarton's ball a la Fran$aise next week ; observe him narrowly, and you will see a true love-knot of white ribbons at his breast ; and if the young lords Maddertie and Fawsyde are there, you will see each with the same gift from the same fond and liberal hand.
